Package com.rb.nonbiz.collections

Class RBMapWithDefault<K,​V>

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.collections.RBMapWithDefault<K,​V>
public class RBMapWithDefault<K,​V>
extends java.lang.Object
Basically just an RBMap, but it also stores a default value, with the semantics that the default value applies when a value for a given key (K) is missing.

If the keys are InstrumentIds, use the specialized version IidMapWithDefault instead.

See Also:
RBMap, RBCategoryMap, RBMapWithOptionalDefault
